    {
      "v": 9,
      "zh": "他 有 三 十 個 兒 子 ， 三 十 女 兒 ； 女 兒 都 嫁 出 去 了 。 他 給 眾 子 從 外 鄉 娶 了 三 十 媳 婦 。 他 作 以 色 列 的 士 師 七 年 。",
      "en": "He had 30 sons. He arranged for 30 of his daughters to be married outside his extended family, and he arranged for 30 young women to be brought from outside as wives for his sons. Ibzan led Israel for seven years;",
